            "summary": "Kids arrive at a marine research station and meet Dr. Marina",
            "text": "The research vessel 'Discovery' rocks gently in the sparkling blue water. {{PLAYER1_NAME}} and {{PLAYER2_NAME}} can hardly believe they're here‚Äîwinners of the Young Scientists Ocean Adventure contest!\n\nDr. Marina Chen, a marine biologist with kind eyes and salt-streaked hair, greets them on deck. 'Welcome aboard! Today, you'll see things most people only dream about. The ocean covers over 70% of our planet, but we've explored less than 20% of it. There are creatures down there we haven't even discovered yet!'\n\nShe leads them to a room filled with equipment. 'We have three expeditions planned. Each will teach you something different about ocean life. But we only have time for one deep dive today.'\n\nThrough the window, {{PLAYER1_NAME}} spots dolphins leaping in the distance. {{PLAYER2_NAME}} notices a large shape moving beneath the surface.",
